{"tid":787341,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"對於不斷搶你工作成果嘅人可以點做","createTime":"2018-08-20T14:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T06:16:30.000Z","uid":174721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9062df561e99cc13f6c5f914109b26bbddc3c7e2","tid":787341,"uid":174721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"喺工作上，有同事不斷咁搶你工作嘅成果，而且有意無意地搶先領功，而上司亦信到十足十，認為本人一啲野都冇做過，到底可以點做。<br />\n而情緒及士氣都因而十分低落，經常訓唔著，愈做愈差，上司就愈黎愈唔信自己，到底可以點做。"},{"pid":"0f528f5853c3d142e29474c1108bbf1096cdee1f","tid":787341,"uid":174721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"其實我想睇開啲，先可以訓好啲。<br />\n生活上無咩人可以講呢啲嘢，覺得一直谷住谷住會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d0d83297d8e3f9ce9450e747461d47a50c8d69","tid":787341,"uid":76931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲嘢冇black and white?<br />\n搶你嗰個同你咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2428d8883b5267534e2c2069a68459c6cd19f234","tid":787341,"uid":174721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"點樣可以睇開啲，有時應該唔好咁介懷先會做得好，但真係睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不斷失眠覺得成日都好唔清醒，夜晚訓覺又有心事銀住銀住，訓下醒下，又或者好似依家咁訓唔著"},{"pid":"d1da6c145927b386921e4c601707e0777fb81124","tid":787341,"uid":128563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:47:33.000Z","msg":"自己憨鳩冇得怨，夠料咪耍手段令到佢辭職囉"},{"pid":"7fddfe958cbc777c4377791543aba0134d4cd105","tid":787341,"uid":174721,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"86d0d83297d8e3f9ce9450e747461d47a50c8d69","tid":787341,"uid":76931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲嘢冇black and white?<br />\n搶你嗰個同你咩關係<img src=\"/asse